# House Price Prediction

## Project Overview
This project uses Machine Learning to predict house prices based on various property features. The project includes data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis (EDA), feature encoding, and training a Linear Regression model for price prediction.

## Dataset
- Dataset: `UK_House_Price_Prediction.csv`
- Features include:
  - Price
  - Date
  - Postcode
  - Property Type
  - New Build Flag
  - Freehold/Leasehold
  - Street
  - Locality
  - Town/City
  - District

## Technologies & Tools
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn

## Machine Learning Model
- Linear Regression

## Workflow
1. Load Dataset
2. Data Cleaning
3. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
4. Feature Encoding
5. Train-Test Split
6. Train Linear Regression Model
7. Model Evaluation
8. House Price Prediction

